00:00:04,969 --> 00:00:12,330
The 48 Laws of Power by Robert Greene
Law number 29: Plan all the way to the End

2
00:00:12,330 --> 00:00:17,859
The ending is everything. Plan all the way
to it, taking into account all the possible

3
00:00:17,859 --> 00:00:22,710
consequences, obstacles, and twists of fortune
that might reverse your hard work and give

4
00:00:22,710 --> 00:00:28,160
the glory to others. By planning to the end
you will not be overwhelmed by circumstances

5
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:34,020
and you will know when to stop. Gently guide
fortune and help determine the future by thinking

6
00:00:34,020 --> 00:00:38,550
