Most men are ruled by the heart, not the head.

7
00:00:38,549 --> 00:00:43,679
Their plans are vague, and when they meet
obstacles they improvise. But improvisation

8
00:00:43,679 --> 00:00:49,719
will only bring you as far as the next crisis,
and is never a substitute for thinking several

